#

Classic Dill Pickles

15 min
$5
50 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackPreservedVegetarian

Description

Crisp, tangy, and refreshing homemade dill pickles that are a perfect snack or condiment.

Ingredients

  • cucumbers: 4 cups, sliced
  • white vinegar: 1 cup
  • water: 1 cup
  • salt: 3 tablespoons
  • sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic cloves: 4, peeled
  • fresh dill: 1 bunch
  • black peppercorns: 1 teaspoon
  • mustard seeds: 1 teaspoon
  • red pepper flakes: 1/2 teaspoon
